author: Graeme Campbell
title: Supreme Unleashes Punky SS17 Editorial in ‘POPEYE’ Magazine
text:
Visit the original post to see all 4 images from this gallery. 
Supreme continues to flex its newly-unveiled SS17 wares with an editorial spread in venerated Tokyo-based magazine POPEYE .
Following last month’s Terry Richardson shoot for Them magazine, the latest campaign was captured by photographer Sandy Kim and features previously-seen pieces including the checkerboard overalls, studded denim jacket, and freaky hockey jersey. From what we can gauge above, the punk cowboy look is very much in.
Peruse the gallery, and look out for Supreme’s web store refreshing today at 11am (EST.)
In other fashion news, The Weeknd has just unveiled a limited edition Starboy collection for European pop-ups.
